Chet Brandenburg https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Chet_Brandenburg 0 Chet Brandenburg (15 October 1897 – 17 July 1974), born James Chester Brandenburg, was an American actor. He appeared in over 400 films between 1924 and 1963. He was born in Kentucky and died in Woodland Hills, Los Angeles. He was the brother of actor Ed Brandenburg.
